<emphasis id="AEE2EAB7FFD8FF9EF86F9A28F70DFEEA" box="[2038,2193,308,333]" pageId="20" pageNumber="325">Taxonomy.</emphasis>
<taxonomicName id="5B964D26FFD8FF9EF7049A28F5A6FEEA" authority="Thomas, 1904" authorityName="Thomas" authorityYear="1904" box="[2205,2618,308,333]" class="Mammalia" family="Herpestidae" genus="Helogale" kingdom="Animalia" order="Carnivora" pageId="20" pageNumber="325" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="hirtula">Helogale hirtula Thomas, 1904</taxonomicName>
, Gabredarre, Kebridar, 
<collectingCountry id="E4817635FFD8FF9EF6AC9A4FF632FED3" box="[2357,2478,339,372]" name="Ethiopia" pageId="20" pageNumber="325">Ethiopia</collectingCountry>
. Previously considered by some authors to comprise two subspecies, 
<taxonomicName id="5B964D26FFD8FF9EF6C59ABEF62FFE64" authorityName="Thomas" authorityYear="1904" box="[2396,2483,418,451]" class="Mammalia" family="Herpestidae" genus="Helogale" kingdom="Animalia" order="Carnivora" pageId="20" pageNumber="325" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="hirtula">hirtula</taxonomicName>
(
<collectingCountry id="E4817635FFD8FF9EF65E9ABEF5A5FE64" box="[2503,2617,418,451]" name="Somalia" pageId="20" pageNumber="325">Somalia</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry id="E4817635FFD8FF9EF86F9AD2F7F3FE4C" box="[2038,2159,462,491]" name="Ethiopia" pageId="20" pageNumber="325">Ethiopia</collectingCountry>
, N. 
<collectingCountry id="E4817635FFD8FF9EF7329AD2F69DFE4C" box="[2219,2305,462,491]" name="Kenya" pageId="20" pageNumber="325">Kenya</collectingCountry>
) and percivalli (C &amp; W 
<collectingCountry id="E4817635FFD8FF9EF86F9AE9F7CEFDB5" box="[2038,2130,501,530]" name="Kenya" pageId="20" pageNumber="325">Kenya</collectingCountry>
). However, a lack of specimens to support subspecific designations makes these doubtful and this species is considered monotypic here.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
